dct_description_sm: Some buildings and sites are shown pictorially. Oriented with north towards upper right. Shows railway, street car, and subway lines. Includes inset map showing direction to former olympic sites: Komazawa Sports Centre and Equestrian Park. Stores and galleries are indexed with reference to their location on map.
